<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>By default, OpenGL supports up to 8 additional clipping planes. Qt3DCore::QClipPlane allows to enable one of these additional planes. These planes can then be manipulated in the shaders using gl_ClipDistance[i] where i varies between 0 and 8.</db:para>
</db:section>
